{
  "stem": "4764.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, to go to the extreme of taking all these people-- there must have been quite a few people-- from one-- one part of Poland to another, herding them there, and saying, well, now, if you've got relatives in somewhere else, you're going to go there.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think you had to pay something, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then say, oh no, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's not all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Back to the ghetto you go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that I remember very well because it was-- it was something that we all sort of looked forward to but it didn't eventuate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember going back to the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember going back to-- back to where we started from.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my feeling throughout all this was always a fear, you see?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had the fear of uniforms, because the German army always were very well dressed with these boots, always shiny, and beautiful uniforms with caps, you see?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- that was something that I feared all my life, even to the-- to a very late age.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was in Australia, I couldn't really relate to anybody in uniform.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It used to always conjure up this picture in me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was the fear of-- of-- of a small child, seeing someone in uniform, in authority.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I've swerved off the topic somewhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to hear that people were actually flogged.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a square there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- I suppose I used to listen to-- to people talking at night, and during the day-- mostly at night, actually-- about what was-- what was happening.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember that they said that quite a few people were either flogged or shot in the square of the-- of this village.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
